Uses of Package
environment.GUI.views

  • Packages that use environment.GUI.views 
    Package Description
    environment
    This module contains the model and the different views for the Petrol Station Simulation.
    environment.GUI
    This module contains all the classes necessary for the graphical user interfaces.
    environment.GUI.views
    This module contains all the classes necessary for displaying the results of the simulation to the user.
  • Classes in environment.GUI.views used by environment 
    Class and Description
    SimulatorView
    The SimulatorView interface is used by classes which deliver information about the status of the simulation.
  • Classes in environment.GUI.views used by environment.GUI 
    Class and Description
    SimulatorView
    The SimulatorView interface is used by classes which deliver information about the status of the simulation.
  • Classes in environment.GUI.views used by environment.GUI.views 
    Class and Description
    Animated
    The Animated class is a subclass of the JFrame which implements the SimulatorView interface.
    Animated.AnimationPanel
    The AnimationaPanel class is a subclass of the JPanel class which is designed for drawing visual representations of the Station objects.
    Animated.TimeStamp
    The Animated.TimeStamp class is a container used for the Animation class to store Station objects and times.
    Animated.Visual
    The interface used to produce the visual representation of the Location.
    Animated.Visualisation
    The Animated.Visualisation enumeration contains visual representations of objects to be displayed in the Animated.AnimationPanel.
    CommandLine
    The CommandLine class displays information of the simulation via the Console (System.out).
    Graph
    A graphical view of the simulation.
    Graph.Entry
    Stores all the Statistics from the Station that is passed to the Graph each tick of the Simulator.
    Graph.GraphPanel
    This Graph.GraphPanel denotes a graph on screen.
    Graph.StatisticType
    All the values and encapsulated functionality of the elements that will be added to the Graph.statisticTypes.
    Graph.VehicleType
    All the values and encapsulated functionality of the elements that will be added to the Graph.vehicleTypes.
    SimulatorView
    The SimulatorView interface is used by classes which deliver information about the status of the simulation.
